    <h2 class="heading">Bubewa:  
    <span class="color1">Ratings </span> and
    <span class="color1">Reviews</span>
    Platform
    </h2>
      <p class ="small"> Saves you money and headaches by working as a community</p>
  </div>
  <hr>

  <p class ="sub-heading"> 

